.SH NAME
cdns_uart_break_ctl \- Based on the input ctl we have to start or stop transmitting char breaks
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" cdns_uart_break_ctl
.BI "(struct uart_port *port "  ","
.BI "int ctl "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "port" 12
Handle to the uart port structure
.IP "ctl" 12
Value based on which start or stop decision is taken
